Description: Implements the Linear Combination Test (LCT) for identifying
    differentially expressed gene sets in high-dimensional gene expression data.
    Supports multiple covariance matrix estimators including shrinkage (Sch√§fer &
    Strimmer, 2005 <doi:10.2202/1544-6115.1175>), ridge regularization (Van Wieringen &
    Peeters, 2016 <doi:10.18637/jss.v070.i03>), graphical lasso (Friedman et al.,
    2008 <doi:10.1093/biostatistics/kxm045>), and adaptive lasso (Rothman et al.,
    2009 <doi:10.1214/08-EJS252>). Designed for robust performance in unbalanced
    study designs with permutation-based significance testing following the
    methodology of Wang et al. (2011) <doi:10.2202/1544-6115.1618>.
